value: The 'Old Railway Hotel' is now a library, but you can still see the old hotel's influence.
The 'Utstikten Tower', from the top of the tallest tower in Storuman you can see the whole of the surrounding area.
The town mascot 'Wildeman', a wooden statue.
Once a year there is a street market called 'Storumandagarna' on the last weekend of June.
In August there is a Folkrace Rally between the towns of Forsvik and Storuman, which is about 15 kilometers in length.
